Adds_Scarlet Lady_Status_Primary Target_: Identified as the focus of a coordinated attack.
Adds_Scarlet Lady_Status_Suppuration_Des: Maximum HP is reduced and damage taken is increased.
Bosse_Suzaku_Status_Love's True Form_Des: Suzaku's heretofore unknown visage is revealed.
ContentDesc_Seelentanz - Suzaku: As the return of the mad auspice Koryu draws ever closer, Genbu of the Four Lords seeks to marshal his comrades' strength. But while the white tiger, Byakko, has been restored to his senses, the radiant Suzaku is on the verge of succumbing to the aramitama. For centuries she has mourned the fallen Tenzen, and in her boundless grief struggled to accept his loss. What is more, her ascendant aramitama now clouds her mind and drives her to reject those who would offer her comfort. As before, there is but one way Suzaku can be brought back from the brink of madness─for the sake of the Ruby Sea and those who call her home, you and your comrades must quell the rage within the auspice's soul.
Instancecontenttextdata_19900_Text: Tenzen? Tenzen, 'tis I! Sheathe your sword, I beg of you!
Instancecontenttextdata_19901_Text: You gave me the strength to rise from the ashes!
Instancecontenttextdata_19902_Text: I never showed you my true form, did I...?
Instancecontenttextdata_19905_Text: All I ever wanted was for you and I to...to...
Instancecontenttextdata_19906_Text: You never did make it easy, did you?
Instancecontenttextdata_19907_Text: We will wake you from this madness!
Instancecontenttextdata_19908_Text: I could not bear to lose you again!
Instancecontenttextdata_19909_Text: Trust in me, my love! I will protect you─I promise!
Instancecontenttextdata_19910_Text: Please, my love─ If only you would listen...
Instancecontenttextdata_19913_Text: If it must be thus, then I'm glad...it is you...
Instancecontenttextdata_19914_Text: Let there be no more secrets between us...
